<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.curtin.edu.au/units/cg201/course_i.html">Curtin U., Computational Geometry 201</A>.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://pine.fernuni-hagen.de/GI/wasist/wasist.html">Was ist
Algorithmische Geometrie?</A>
Auszug aus dem Kurs <I>Algorithmische Geometrie</I> der
FernUniversitï¿½t Hagen.
(In German.)
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.jhu.edu/~goodrich/teach/geom/">Johns Hopkins, 600.488, Computational Geometry</A>.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ecse.rpi.edu/Courses/S96/35679/index.html">Rensselaer Polytechnic, ECSE 35.679, Computational Geometry</A>.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://Theory.Stanford.EDU/~jbasch/cs368/">Stanford U., Geometric Algorithms, cs368</A>.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.ubc.ca/dept/grad/courses/1995/516">U. British Columbia, CPSC 516, Computational Geometry</A>
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/164/">U.C. Irvine, Computational Geometry, ICS 164</A>, and <A HREF="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~eppstein/266/">Graduate Computational Geometry, ICS 266</A>.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.uiowa.edu/~sriram/compgeom.html">U. Iowa, Computational Geometry 22C:196</A>.
<P>
<LI> <A HREF="http://www.geom.umn.edu/~math5337/">U. Minn., Math 5337</A>.
Computational methods in elementary geometry.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.cs.ruu.nl/docs/vakken/geo/index.html">Geometrische Algoritmen</A>.
Info on a course in computational geometry at Utrecht.
(In Dutch.)
</UL>
<P>
<B>Courses and course material from geometric applications:</B>
<P><UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.eng.auburn.edu/department/cse/classes/cse690/mccreary690.html">CSE690: Graph Drawing Seminar</A>, Auburn U.
<P>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.gsd.harvard.edu/~malcolm/DDM/DDMmain.html">
Digital Design Media</A> online textbook.
<P>
<!-- not responding 16 Sep 1996 -->
<LI><A HREF="http://www.icsi.berkeley.edu/cs267/lecture18/lecture18.html">Graph partitioning</A>.
Geometric methods for finding graph separators.
Lecture notes from CS267, UC Berkeley, on high performance computing.
This problem has applications in scientific computation,
and, apparently, in DNA sequencing.
<P>
</UL><HR><P>
